        "Text": "Welcome to U.S. Treasury. Press 1 for IRS, 2 for U.S. Mint, 3 for Bureau of Fiscal Service, 4 for Treasury Direct, or 5 for Direct Express."
      },
      "Transitions": {"NextAction": "get-bureau"}
    },
